  26,62,Qala kalla inna maAAiya rabbee sayahdeeni
  26,63,Faawhayna ila moosa ani idrib biAAasaka albahra fainfalaqa fakana kullu firqin kaalttawdi alAAatheemi
  26,64,Waazlafna thamma alakhareena
